What we do

   Trust-IT is an international marketing & research organisation
   specialised in fostering Information and Communication Technology
   solutions Europe and globally. Trust-IT is a multi-national team,
   highly skilled in creating communication, digital web strategies and
   software for today‚Äôs digital environment, be that for business,
   research & science or public sector organisations. Trust-IT can support
   you in carrying out feasibility and market studies, design reports,
   sustainability activities & business models.
   Read more


Open House

   Every Year, Trust-IT jointly hosts its ‚ÄúAperitivo with the Artists Open
   House‚Äù together with by PI Management, Trust -IT Services, COMMpla &
   Innotec. We proudly open our offices to the public to view talented
   artists artwork. You get to meet the person behind their work on
   display, socialise and make new acquaintances. Photography, Art, &
   technology blended together in our homely environment we call ‚Äúwork‚Äù
   every day and we are engulfed with beautiful art that stays with us all
   year around in amongst the language of ICT Technology & Communications.
   Read more


